{"tid":2127731,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"是咁的 我做地盤","createTime":"2020-07-27T13:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T14:09:01.000Z","uid":123920,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0bec673ab0bc528fe13a333b89bc8c12758c6998","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我做地盤。<br />\n今日晏晝放飯，我買咗碗牛腩河加啤酒。<br />\n「阿哥，無咗堂食喎。」粉麵店阿姐話。<br />\n「得喇！阿叔我單手拎住黎食！男人老狗，我唔驚熱既！」我。<br />\n阿姐冷笑咗一聲。<br />\n當我行出麵店，打算去附近公園坐低慢慢嘆。<br />\n我心諗，你班香港人真係唔捱得，外國人都係咁樣野餐咋！<br />\n點知&hellip;公園被紅膠帶封晒，唔講以為入面有命案發生。<br />\n算數！我行過去人少少嘅路邊食！<br />\n正當我打開個麵，諗起一個問題。<br />\n仆街&hellip;戶外口罩令，我一除低咗，咪犯法囉？！<br />\n話口未完，冚家富貴落雨！！我即刻閂返個蓋保護住碗牛腩河，連個天都玩鳩我！<br />\n唔緊要！我去商場啲後樓梯食！<br />\n好多廚房佬，晏晝落場都去嗰啲地方訓覺，仲有冷氣！不知幾爽！<br />\n點知，我一打開商場後門，見到已經有兩條友喺度食緊飯。<br />\n「室內限聚令兩人啊，過主啦！」其中一個話。<br />\n於是，我行晒成個區所有屋苑、商場&hellip;全部後樓梯都被人霸晒。<br />\n最後，我只好入去商場廁所，每格都有兩個人食緊飯！<br />\n我想食個飯啫，點解要咁對我喎？！<br />\n「你唔介意嘅入去食囉。」清潔廁所嘅阿叔，打開廁所放雜物嗰格畀我入去食飯。<br />\n我入到去，搬開啲雜物，坐咗喺廁所板。<br />\n突然間，一陣臭味傳過黎，隔籬廁格條仆街，食完飯即刻屙！<br />\n算數，我真係好肚餓&hellip;<br />\n我打開碗牛腩河，啲麵脹鳩晒！筷子夾極都夾唔起！<br />\n我飲咗一啖已經唔凍嘅啤酒，好苦，好澀<br />\n好似我人生一樣咁苦澀。<br />\n幾十歲人，我有咩苦未捱過？<br />\n我淨係唔想犯法，同埋食碗牛腩河啫&hellip;點解都咁囉啊？<br />\n嗰一刻，我忍唔住喊咗出嚟。<br />\n我唔敢抹眼淚，因為我啱啱先醒起，我唔記得洗手。<br />\n（完）<br />\n後記：<br />\n屌你老味弱智政府，我連寫個故都覺得自己唔合邏輯。<br />\n大家都知疫情好多嘢都唔方便，但大佬啊，你啲政策用吓腦吖<br />\n畀少少同理心唔會好難嘛？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/181821911903965/posts/3164359466983513/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F181821911903965%2Fposts%2F3164359466983513%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=e230831b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/181821911903965/posts/3164359466983513/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"1b2607f86b9d0d5de2c150d35d890b595a8a0b3a","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b290de8f58f0324d9e4346044f503c04fa2924","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbf8e1649dce960ea8f009e28f158dcc4de5d2b","tid":2127731,"uid":147770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"犯法咪犯法 除非你係警察"},{"pid":"7f018a78d2a81bc1fb723aca049f2e0334df28ff","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56104891f2a83ca4c362c5f142665a4ef5425e86","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6763777eebcb6668d6fc5af93eb67069205ab23","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99abfd1aa309710154c4a1209a65d1a08601772d","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d282227f26435cfd55f778b6f250ed2564168da1","tid":2127731,"uid":181025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"On 撚9 政府！ <br />\n辛苦地盤工人😣😣😣"},{"pid":"dc8b2d6128634e53a5df033f63468c9265d1d277","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86656b44b50bac699f7481f287d87f61386e069c","tid":2127731,"uid":217433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:06:11.000Z","msg":"辛9苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b8eeba3d2fe8944a1bdf5621602914a0905d13","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b80f4db92b90403b927727ac8371597929f576","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4564beb1edcc09da1a1bb148cd70aba1705f80","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1924b450e443d30ac360236a9759eb1e2a4c980","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0d2d21184c1706bfdfb97945bf05c2e6c2a0c9","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8907d6c62a10ab220c5bf45e0763a8e570089fa","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3b8dcb08e3f922f79026deff40f29c3ba39b11","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfa550c2e509f52c611a5dbcde80af65a329bf8","tid":2127731,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2b1ff0c7143a2a581b078dd514b682ab7d173f","tid":2127731,"uid":144009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"星期三廁格見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}